TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct LP."NAME" as ApplicationName, LP.SHORT_NAME as ProjectAcronym, LU."NAME" as UCAName, LUX.USER_NAME as lastModifiedByUser, count(distinct LDMR.MSG_ID) as messageCount from LSW_DUR_MSG_RECEIVED LDMR, LSW_UCA LU, LSW_USR_XREF LUX, LSW_PO_REFERENCE LPR, LSW_SNAPSHOT LS, LSW_PROJECT LP where LU.UCA_ID = LDMR.UCA_ID and LUX.USER_ID = LU.LAST_MODIFIED_BY_USER_ID and LU.PROCESS_REF = LPR.REFERENCE_ID and LPR.BRANCH_ID = LS.BRANCH_ID and LS.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID and LDMR.CORRELATION_KEY not in (select distinct LIMI.CORRELATION_KEY from LSW_INST_MSG_INCL LIMI ) group by LP."NAME", LP.SHORT_NAME, LU."NAME", LUX.USER_NAME
